{% extends "base.html" %}

{% block title %}YBG Security Network - 보안 네트워크{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<div class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl w-full">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold mb-4 text-green-400 font-mono">YBG</h1>
            <h2 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-green-300">(주)융보공 연락 플랫폼</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-green-500 opacity-80">YBG Cyber Security Hacker's Platform</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
            <div class="bg-black bg-opacity-60 border border-green-500 rounded-lg p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-green-400">🔐 보안 접속 정보</h3>
                <div class="space-y-3">
                    <div class="bg-gray-900 p-3 rounded font-mono text-sm">
                        <span class="text-green-600">접속자 식별코드:</span><br>
                        <span class="text-green-400">{{ encoded_message }}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-black bg-opacity-60 border border-green-500 rounded-lg p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-green-400">🌐 네트워크 경로</h3>
                <div class="space-y-3">
                    <div class="bg-gray-900 p-3 rounded font-mono text-sm">
                        <span class="text-green-600">암호화된 접속 경로:</span><br>
                        <span class="text-green-400 break-all">{{ encoded_path }}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-black bg-opacity-60 border border-green-500 rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-green-400">접속 안내</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-left max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                <p class="text-green-300">• 올바른 해커에게 요청을 전송하세요</p>
                <p class="text-green-300">• 필요한 정보를 명확히 요구하세요</p>
                <p class="text-green-300">• 올바른 페이지에 접속하세요</p>
                <p class="text-green-300">• 보안 프로토콜을 준수하세요</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-8">
                <div class="inline-block bg-green-900 bg-opacity-50 border border-green-400 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg">
                    <span class="text-green-400 font-mono">주소창을 사용하여 연락 페이지로 직접 이동하세요</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
            <p class="text-green-600 text-sm opacity-60">
                Unauthorized access is prohibited. All activities are monitored.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}